init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world said that they didn't know what happened to the US.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: a virus that caused them to go into a rage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: turned into something called "Neo Zombies", which were humans that possessed superhuman strength and agility.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world then says that they need to perform an inspection of the US and if they find anything wrong, they will treat them as a rogue state.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They did this by taking blood samples and giving the US people exams, as well as looking at their homes.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: that the virus is dead and that the US should be let out of isolation and allowed to rejoin the world.
